---
import {Heart, Lightbulb, Zap, Sun } from '@lucide/astro';
---

<section id="beneficios" class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Header de la sección -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
        ¿Cómo puedo ayudarte?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Descubre los beneficios únicos de trabajar conmigo y cómo la psicología cuántica 
        puede transformar tu vida de manera profunda y duradera.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid de beneficios -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      
      <!-- Beneficio 1 -->
      <div class="group bg-soft rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:shadow-soft transition-all duration-300">
          <Heart class="w-5 h-5 text-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Sanación Emocional</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Libérate de traumas y patrones emocionales que limitan tu crecimiento personal.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Beneficio 2 -->
      <div class="group bg-soft rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-secondary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-secondary group-hover:shadow-soft transition-all duration-300">
          <Lightbulb class="w-5 h-5 text-secondary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Despertar Cuántico</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Conecta con tu verdadero potencial y transforma tu realidad desde el nivel cuántico.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Beneficio 3 -->
      <div class="group bg-soft rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-accent group-hover:shadow-soft transition-all duration-300">
          <Zap class="w-5 h-5 text-accent group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Propósito de Vida</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Descubre tu misión única y alinea tus acciones con tu verdadero propósito.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Beneficio 4 -->
      <div class="group bg-soft rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white hover:shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:border-primary/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-warm/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-warm group-hover:shadow-soft transition-all duration-300">
          <Sun class="w-5 h-5 text-warm group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Equilibrio Interior</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Encuentra armonía entre mente, cuerpo y espíritu para vivir en plenitud.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>